sub_title: Teacher of English as a second language.
summary:
My name is Hugh, a British native-speaker with many years of teaching experience. I have enjoyed the benefits of an international education and the experience of having lived in various countries (The UK, France, Malta and The Netherlands). 

I am based in Amsterdam and I look forward to teaching You English in this dynamic city!
